requestBody.description:
Format varies depending on the consumed content type application/merge-patch+json or application/json-patch+json
Tool for creating a patch object https://chbrown.github.io/rfc6902/

Examples:
application/merge-patch+json  An partial object but with the modified values is sent
{
    "name":"new name 1767019080203",
    "description": "Updated descritption"
}

application/json-patch+json An array of operations that will be performed on the object
[
    {
        "op": "replace",
        "path": "/name",
        "value": "Christopher Brown"
    },
    {
        "op": "replace",
        "path": "/description",
        "value": "item description"
    }
],

